sections.text: without a license; penalty.Any person required to be licensed under the Delayed Deposit Services Licensing Act who operates a delayed deposit services business in this state without first obtaining a license under the act or while such license is suspended or revoked by the director shall be guilty of a Class IV felony.SourceLaws 1994, LB 967, ยง 26.
